SQL Hunting Dog was the original Quick Search Add-In for SQL Server
Management Studio. While SQL Pilot is an independent implementation
built from scratch, it owes its concept and design inspiration to the
pioneering work of the SQL Hunting Dog team.

We also acknowledge the contributions of the SQL Hunting Dog community,
including PR authors pstraszak, FastNinja, and pklejnowski, whose work
on SSMS 2016/2017 support informed our understanding of SSMS extension
evolution.
